data.description: Investor special! Bring your contractor and your best ideas to finish out this diamond in the rough. There's no need for convincing on the outside with a wonderfully private 5 acre lot. All that is needed is to make the inside shine and watch this property turn into something completely new! This property has so much potential the only worry is having too many ideas on how to complete it.
